flowchart TD
    Login([Admin login]) --> Panel[Dashboard admin<br/>RBAC: role=admin]

    Panel --> KB[Curadoria Knowledge Base]
    Panel --> Users[Gestão de usuários]
    Panel --> ML[Retreino do modelo ML]
    Panel --> Search[Busca semântica]
    Panel --> Obs[Painéis de observabilidade]

    KB --> IngURL[POST /api/v1/ingestion/url<br/>Crawl4AI + Playwright]
    KB --> IngDoc[POST /api/v1/ingestion/doc<br/>Docling]
    IngURL --> Chunk[Chunking + embeddings]
    IngDoc --> Chunk
    Chunk --> ChromaWrite[(ChromaDB<br/>cashme_kb)]

    Users --> CRUD[POST /api/v1/admin/users<br/>RBAC: cliente · analista · admin]
    CRUD --> PG[(Postgres<br/>tabela users · bcrypt)]

    ML --> Train[POST /api/v1/credit/finetune<br/>scripts/train_model.py]
    Train --> Pipeline[SklearnCreditScorer.train<br/>RandomForest + StandardScaler<br/>108 features]
    Pipeline --> AUC[AUC-ROC · feature_importance]
    Pipeline --> Save[(./data/credit_model.pkl)]
    Pipeline --> MLflow[(MLflow tracking<br/>cashme-credit-scorer)]

    Search --> SearchAPI[GET /api/v1/search?q=...]
    SearchAPI --> Hybrid[Híbrido<br/>ChromaDB + BM25]
    Hybrid --> Results[Top-K + scores]

    Obs --> Graf[Grafana<br/>dashboards: host · containers<br/>postgres · redis · loki · tempo]
    Obs --> LF[Langfuse v3<br/>traces · custos · graph view]
    Obs --> MLF2[MLflow UI<br/>experiments · runs · artifacts]

    classDef store fill:#e8f4ff,stroke:#0a66c2,stroke-width:2px;
    classDef ml fill:#fff4e6,stroke:#d97706,stroke-width:2px;
    classDef obs fill:#f3e8ff,stroke:#7c3aed,stroke-width:2px;
    class ChromaWrite,PG,Save,MLflow store
    class Pipeline,Train ml
    class Graf,LF,MLF2 obs
